  "instructions": [
    "Combine flour, sugar, and yeast in a bowl. ",
    "Add warm milk and mix until a smooth batter forms. ",
    "Beat in eggs and melted butter. ",
    "Knead the dough for 5 minutes. ",
    "Rest the dough for 1 hour. ",
    "Divide the dough into 8 equal pieces. ",
    "Roll each piece into a ball. ",
    "Flatten a ball slightly and place a mozzarella ball in the center. ",
    "Top with grated carrot and zucchini. ",
    "Close the dough around the filling, pressing edges to seal. ",
    "Heat a tava-griddle over medium-high heat. ",
    "Cook fritters for 2-3 minutes on each side. ",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
  ],
